    "description": "<strong>开局游戏若遇黑屏，可按下组合键 alt + s 跳过。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2>《罗刹封魔传》是由exeCUTE开发，GAMER Plan发行的和风动作游戏。<br><br>江户时代。妖魔，人类，神共存的世界。<br>拥有强大封魔之力的鬼族公主「罗刹来希」，<br>通过施展个性十足的【剑技】，以及广域【结界术】击败出现于眼前的敌人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>丰富的战斗动作，可快速移动，抢占优势，连续攻击。<br></li><li>攻守兼备的各式【剑技】！通过多样的组合达到应对不同战斗的绝佳效果！<br></li><li>除【剑技】外，更有驱使符咒发动的火，风，雷各属性【结界术】，以范围攻击压制敌群！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844400/extras/3465f0ff1fcbc994146d030fbca2f674.poster.avif?t=1729130275\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844400/extras/3465f0ff1fcbc994146d030fbca2f674.webm?t=1729130275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844400/extras/3465f0ff1fcbc994146d030fbca2f674.mp4?t=1729130275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844400/extras/1fd7b7290be22d272f5804af9cb85527.poster.avif?t=1729130275\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844400/extras/1fd7b7290be22d272f5804af9cb85527.webm?t=1729130275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844400/extras/1fd7b7290be22d272f5804af9cb85527.mp4?t=1729130275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>玩家可在游戏中将以上要素自由组合，<br>打造出只属于自己的战斗方式。<br>尽情享受每一场畅快的和风战斗吧！",
